result.title: Training 11
result.content:
Salam.

Be ellat in ke ta mooddati kelas nakhahim dasht, seri jadid tamrin ha ezafe shod.

Soalat in tamrin nesbat be tamrin haye ghabli sakht tar hastand va ba estefade az chiz hayi ke be shoma dars dade shode mitooind halleshan konid.

Hamchenin agar soalat ziadi baraye shoma sakht hastand say konid bishtar baraye tamrin haye ghabli vaght begozarid.

Movaffagh bashid.
